skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crypto price
des:
Crypto Price will tell you the latest value of common cryptocurrencies in US Dollars.
The current version supports: Ethereum, Bitcoin, Tether, Ripple, Litecoin, Cardano, and Polkadot. More currencies will be added soon.

Disclaimer: Crypto Price provides an estimate of the current market price in USD within the last 5 minutes. Note Crypto Price should not be relied upon for making investment decisions, but simply to provide an indication of the latest price.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
